Li Ka-Shing Purchases 500,000 Shares in Cheung Kong

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-09-22T00:01:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/li-ka-shing-bought-cheung-kong-500-000-shares-on-sept-19.html
(Corrects currency in first paragraph of story dated Sept.
21.)  Cheung Kong (Holdings) Ltd.
Chairman  Li Ka-Shing  bought 500,000 shares of the company at an
average price of HK$96.589 each on Sept. 19, according to a
disclosure filing to the Hong Kong stock exchange.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Lui at 
 mlui11@bloomberg.net  